{"bangumi":{"date":"2009-06-13","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/73/60/10581_wt21d.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/73/60/10581_wt21d.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/73/60/10581_wt21d.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/73/60/10581_wt21d.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/73/60/10581_wt21d.jpg"},"summary":"讲述的是名闻遐迩的剑客——宫本武藏。17岁前，恶贯乡里，不知生之意义。17岁后，远赴关原之战，死里逃生。又被泽庵和尚捆绑于千年杉上、囚于天守阁中，而后重获生命、茅塞顿开。以艰难当饼、以困苦当水，足迹遍历日本各地。曾与66位高手比武，皆获全胜，尤以打败名剑客佐佐木小次郎的“岩流岛之战”震烁古今！一个苦其心志的修行武者，一位17世纪的剑道家，一名400年前的传奇人物。晚年，宫本武藏在熊本市近郊金峰山的灵岩洞中，将自己的一生以及独创的“二天一流”的剑法，记录了下来，那本书就是后来成为了传世名作的《五轮书》。","name":"宮本武蔵 -双剣に馳せる夢-","name_cn":"宫本武藏 双剑驰骋之梦","tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":70,"total_cont":0},{"name":"押井守","count":67,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Production.I.G","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009","count":45,"total_cont":0},{"name":"西久保瑞穂","count":26,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":25,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中泽一登","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"历史","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"西久保瑞穗","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"宫本武藏","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ProductionI.G","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黄濑和哉","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"纪录片","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"アニメ映画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"映画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"独立剧场版","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"黄瀬和哉","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009年","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"补番","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"00","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Production_I.G","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国本武春","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"09春","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"橋本浩一","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"新世纪OVA及剧场","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中澤一登","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":